{"tid":491804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鎅刀男死因研訊】債仔妻爆死者風流史釀悲劇 官：不負責任","createTime":"2017-12-07T01:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T03:29:59.000Z","uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d00c84563192beaf23ed2a8cc17bd71074602c8b","tid":491804,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:15:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171207&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57550318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171207%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57550318&d=dROWvDezH3xzRK1reZmPt10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a7a0e0ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171207%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57550318&h=0734ef7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171207&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57550318</a><br />\n案發前，死者妻子黃敏華向死者朋友羅焌賢追債，雙方理論時，朋友妻子蘇昕穎卻突然爆出死者曾經「背妻媾女」，結果導致黃攜子離家。死者被擊斃後，黃埋怨蘇，為何叫死者去尋妻，蘇反指摘黃推卸責任。死因裁判官昨不禁質問蘇，會否覺得是因她的說話，令小事變成悲劇，甚至變得「戲劇性、好無稽」，認為事件不應該發生。<br />\n<br />\n條死肥閪都算極品港女，為轉移視線唔想還一千蚊，拆散人地屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認撚住條死肥閪<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1960000/1963923/winn1205006_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1960000%2F1963923%2Fwinn1205006_1024_1024.jpg&h=5041fe91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59e29f38e169a094c9165e6b6f47a3a89eb05274","tid":491804,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"寧教人打仔莫教人分妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4528d144e052245d2455c2e3df7870806ef30d6c","tid":491804,"uid":59987,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"相由心生。內心醜陋外形恐怖"},{"pid":"d692aef66bc5a7f8508e5e4ed7cec6704db9dae4","tid":491804,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0